OL,3,CReporting on Storm Desmond while the
OL,4,Cfloods hit home
OL,6,FAs the rain fell and the rivers rose
OL,7,Fin December 2015 I spent the evening
OL,8,Fas the only guest in a hotel in Hawick.
OL,10,FAs I filmed residents around the River
OL,11,FTeviot battled to save what they could
OL,12,Fand move what they carry upstairs, I
OL,13,Fhad more than half a mind wishing I
OL,14,Fcould do the same myself.
OL,16,FI had only just moved into my house
OL,17,Foff Warwick Road in Carlisle where
OL,18,Fsome of the worst flooding was
OL,19,Fbeginning to be reported.
