OL,3,CReporting on Storm Desmond while the
OL,4,Cfloods hit home
OL,6,FIn the days to come the streets would
OL,7,Fbe full of furniture and fittings
OL,8,Fdestroyed by the water and residents
OL,9,Ftried to begin the long and painful
OL,10,Fprocess of pulling out what was
OL,11,Fdamaged beyond repair and replacing it.
OL,13,FFor days afterwards there was no
OL,14,Fpower, and while I reported on the
OL,15,Ffloods by day, my evenings were spent
OL,16,Feating my dinner in the pubs and
OL,17,Frestaurants on Botchergate while
OL,18,Fcharging my phone for the next day's
OL,19,Fupdates.
