OL,3,CReporting on Storm Desmond while the
OL,4,Cfloods hit home
OL,6,FReturning home by torchlight I
OL,7,Fremember how dark it was on Greystone
OL,8,FRoad without street lights, and how
OL,9,Fquiet it was with so many of my
OL,10,Fneighbours having decamped to friends
OL,11,For family during the early stages of
OL,12,Fthe rebuild.
