OL,3,CReporting on Storm Desmond while the
OL,4,Cfloods hit home
OL,6,FIt did bring the community together in
OL,7,Fthe way only a crisis can. Neighbours
OL,8,Fsupported each other in gutting their
OL,9,Fhomes, churches and community centres
OL,10,Fopened their doors to people with
OL,11,Fnowhere else to go, and even Carlisle
OL,12,FUnited's football players took to the
OL,13,Fstreets to offer their help to those
OL,14,Fin need.
