OL,3,CReporting on Storm Desmond while the
OL,4,Cfloods hit home
OL,6,FI know I am not alone in feeling wary
OL,7,Fwhen winter comes and the rain falls
OL,8,Fhard. We all know that since 2015
OL,9,Fmillions have been spent on flood
OL,10,Fdefences, but that was also true in
OL,11,Fthe aftermath of the floods of 2005.
